{
  "uid": "etl-pipeline-observability",
  "title": "ETL Pipeline Observability",
  "description": "Live data-quality view of the food-product ETL pipeline.",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "time": {
    "from": "now-24h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "tags": [
    "etl",
    "pipeline",
    "observability"
  ],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "source",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "Source",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
        },
        "query": "label_values({__name__=~\"etl_dq_score_post|etl_block_dq_score\",source!~\"20|21|branded|foundation\"}, source)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".+",
        "multi": true,
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 3
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Food-Product ETL Pipeline\n\nRaw CSVs from **USDA**, **openFDA**, **OpenFoodFacts**, and **ESCI** are cleaned block-by-block, then enriched in a three-tier cascade (**S1 rules \u2192 S2 KNN \u2192 S3 LLM**). The **DQ score** (0\u2013100) measures completeness and validity \u2014 watch it rise from 'Before' to 'After'."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Final DQ Score per Source (Post-Pipeline)",
      "description": "Data-quality score after the full pipeline. Each bar is one source. Green \u2265 80 = production-ready, yellow 60\u201380 = usable, red < 60 = needs attention.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 6
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "valueMode": "color",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "decimals": 1,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "red"
              },
              {
                "value": 60,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 80,
                "color": "green"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "label_replace(max by (source) (etl_dq_score_post{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source\", \"(.*)\") or label_replace(max by (source_name) (etl_dq_score_post{source_name=~\"$source\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source_name\", \"(.*)\")",
          "legendFormat": "{{src}}",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "LLM Cost per Source (USD)",
      "description": "Cumulative spend on LLM enrichment calls (tier S3) per source. The pipeline prefers cheaper tiers (S1 rules, S2 KNN) first, so this should stay small \u2014 watch for spikes that indicate S1/S2 are failing.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 37,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "valueMode": "text",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 4,
          "min": 0,
          "noValue": "No LLM calls yet \u2014 S1/S2 resolved every row (this is the healthy case \u2714)",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "green"
              },
              {
                "value": 0.1,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 1,
                "color": "red"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "label_replace(max by (source) (etl_llm_cost_usd_total{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"} > 0), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source\", \"(.*)\") or label_replace(max by (source_name) (etl_llm_cost_usd_total{source_name=~\"$source\"} > 0), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source_name\", \"(.*)\")",
          "legendFormat": "{{src}}",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "DQ Score: Before vs After Pipeline",
      "description": "Per source: raw input quality (orange, Before) vs final quality (green, After). The gap is the lift the pipeline delivers.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 10
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "basic",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "valueMode": "text",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "decimals": 1,
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byRegexp",
              "options": "/^Before/"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "orange"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byRegexp",
              "options": "/^After/"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "label_replace(max by (source) (etl_dq_score_pre{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source\", \"(.*)\") or label_replace(max by (source_name) (etl_dq_score_pre{source_name=~\"$source\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source_name\", \"(.*)\")",
          "legendFormat": "Before \u00b7 {{src}}",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "label_replace(max by (source) (etl_dq_score_post{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source\", \"(.*)\") or label_replace(max by (source_name) (etl_dq_score_post{source_name=~\"$source\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source_name\", \"(.*)\")",
          "legendFormat": "After \u00b7 {{src}}",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "barchart",
      "title": "Enrichment Tier Breakdown",
      "description": "How each row's missing fields were filled. S1 (rules) is cheap, S2 (KNN) is medium, S3 (LLM) is expensive, Unresolved means no strategy worked. A healthy pipeline resolves most rows at S1.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 10
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "xTickLabelRotation": 0,
        "showValue": "always",
        "stacking": "normal",
        "groupWidth": 0.7,
        "barWidth": 0.9,
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        },
        "xField": "src"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0,
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short",
          "noValue": "No enrichment data yet \u2014 these runs didn't include the enrich_stage (no enrichment_columns in the schema)"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "S1 rules"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "green"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "S2 KNN"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "blue"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "S3 LLM"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "purple"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byName",
              "options": "Unresolved"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": {
                  "mode": "fixed",
                  "fixedColor": "red"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "S1",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "label_replace(max by (source) (etl_enrichment_s1_resolved{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source\", \"(.*)\") or label_replace(max by (source_name) (etl_enrichment_s1_resolved{source_name=~\"$source\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source_name\", \"(.*)\")",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "S2",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "label_replace(max by (source) (etl_enrichment_s2_resolved{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source\", \"(.*)\") or label_replace(max by (source_name) (etl_enrichment_s2_resolved{source_name=~\"$source\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source_name\", \"(.*)\")",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "S3",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "label_replace(max by (source) (etl_enrichment_s3_resolved{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source\", \"(.*)\") or label_replace(max by (source_name) (etl_enrichment_s3_resolved{source_name=~\"$source\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source_name\", \"(.*)\")",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "refId": "UN",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "label_replace(max by (source) (etl_enrichment_unresolved{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source\", \"(.*)\") or label_replace(max by (source_name) (etl_enrichment_unresolved{source_name=~\"$source\"}), \"src\", \"$1\", \"source_name\", \"(.*)\")",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "job": true,
              "run_id": true,
              "status": true,
              "source": true,
              "source_name": true
            },
            "renameByName": {}
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "joinByField",
          "options": {
            "byField": "src",
            "mode": "outer"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "renameByRegex",
          "options": {
            "regexp": "^Value #S1$",
            "renamePattern": "S1 rules"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "renameByRegex",
          "options": {
            "regexp": "^Value #S2$",
            "renamePattern": "S2 KNN"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "renameByRegex",
          "options": {
            "regexp": "^Value #S3$",
            "renamePattern": "S3 LLM"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "renameByRegex",
          "options": {
            "regexp": "^Value #UN$",
            "renamePattern": "Unresolved"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "barchart",
      "title": "Block-by-Block DQ Progress",
      "description": "DQ after each cleaning block in execution order. Each bar group is one source; each bar is one block. The staircase shows quality rising as whitespace, noise, and schema issues get fixed.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 11
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "vertical",
        "xTickLabelRotation": -35,
        "xTickLabelSpacing": 0,
        "showValue": "auto",
        "stacking": "none",
        "groupWidth": 0.85,
        "barWidth": 0.9,
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi"
        },
        "xField": "label"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "decimals": 2,
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "color": {
            "mode": "continuous-GrYlRd"
          }
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
          },
          "expr": "max by (source, block_name, block_seq) (etl_block_dq_score{source=~\"$source\",source!~\"20|21\"})",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {
              "Time": true,
              "__name__": true,
              "job": true,
              "run_id": true,
              "status": true
            },
            "renameByName": {
              "Value": "DQ"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "calculateField",
          "options": {
            "mode": "reduceRow",
            "alias": "label",
            "reduce": {
              "reducer": "allValues"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "merge",
          "options": {}
        }
      ]
    },
